    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Rivigo South Asia Partners - Attractive Package",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Rivigo South Asia Partners. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Allahabad-based team.\n\nAbout Rivigo South Asia Partners:\nRivigo South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rivigo South Asia Partners!",
